For an online (web-form) valdator for .travis.yml files:
https://config.travis-ci.com/explore

----------------

For the command-line client:

sudo apt -yqq install ruby`ruby -e 'puts RUBY_VERSION[/\d+\.\d+/]'`-dev
sudo gem install travis
OR:
sudo gem install travis --no-rdoc --no-ri


